title: 325F.988 NONAPPLICATION.
text: Sections 325F.985 to 325F.987 do not apply to private label goods manufactured according to the purchaser's proprietary specifications. Sections 325F.986 and 325F.987 shall not be construed to grant a private label manufacturer any rights of ownership or use of a brand, trademark or commercial indicia that is owned by another person including a private label purchaser or its assignee.
